1.8
log
@Convert watchdog(4) devices to use autoconf(9) framework.

ok deraadt, tests on glxpcib and ok mpi
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: tcpcib.c,v 1.7 2013/12/06 21:03:04 deraadt Exp $	*/

/*
